    },
    "AR uses the camera for a real-world overlay. Immersive shows a pure black sky driven by the gyroscope. Free-look lets you drag to look around." : {
      "comment" : "The footer for the \"Sky view\" section of the settings.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "machine_translated",
            "value" : "AR usa la cámara para superponer el cielo real. Inmersivo muestra un cielo completamente negro controlado por el giroscopio. Vista libre te permite arrastrar para mirar a tu alrededor."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Astronomy only needs your rough position — a city-level fix is plenty." : {
      "localizations" : {
