    "Star data: Yale Bright Star Catalogue and the HYG database (CC BY-SA 4.0). Deep-sky: Messier, Caldwell & NGC. Ephemerides: Meeus / JPL. Satellite elements: Celestrak. Planet textures: Solar System Scope (CC BY 4.0)." : {
